textContent:
Gil wants and needs Financial stability safety and believes the path to do that is to have two stable jobs that aren't an income and then in the spare time all the energy spent exploring, traveling and experiencing the world 

Aaron wants and needs to express by creating and starting things which naturally have risk and uncertainty. So Aaron wants the freedom to be able to start his companies and use the money to explore and travel the world. 

The conditions that need to be achieved are Financial stability, certainty, and time to be together.
